npc/laras: Past this point there's only the core — the thing every part of this machine answers to.
npc/laras: It isn't a person. It's the entire logic of this place made solid, and it was built to never, ever let go.
npc/laras: You've seen what it does now — to the wallet, and to the mind. The last stretch is about how people actually get free of it.
npc/laras: Before you go to end this, make sure you understand exactly what you're ending. If you want to test yourself first, just ask me.
